        <abstract> 
<p>CD is delighted that JVC will undertake translation of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p>  
<p>Agrees with JVC’s opinion of Haeckel’s book [<hi rend="italic">Generelle Morphologie</hi> (1866)]. CD believes it is bad policy for Haeckel to speak so positively about a disputed theory [i.e., CD’s] and particularly regrets the severity of EH’s criticisms of other authors.</p> 
        </abstract>
